{"id": "30985", "revid": "773742", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=30985", "title": "Fractal Blade", "text": "The Fractal Blade is an &lt;a href=\"short%20sword\"&gt;short sword&lt;/a&gt; that appears in \"\". It can be found hidden deep inside the cave complex in the &lt;a href=\"Forest%20of%20Wyrms\"&gt;Forest of Wyrms&lt;/a&gt;.\nAcquisition.\nThis powerful short sword can be found in the &lt;a href=\"Ruined%20Temple%20of%20Bhaal\"&gt;Ruined Temple of Bhaal&lt;/a&gt;, after solving &lt;a href=\"Sarevok\"&gt;Sarevok&lt;/a&gt;'s &lt;a href=\"Sarevok%27s%20Secret\"&gt;mask riddle&lt;/a&gt;. The hallway before the reliquary\u2019s antechamber has six masks on the wall, two rows of three. The description reads:\n\"Six gigantic domino masks are set into this wall. No eyes peer at you from them, yet you cannot escape the feeling you are being observed.\"\nClick on the \"third\", \"first\" and \"fourth\" masks as per the &lt;a href=\"Page%20from%20Sarevok%27s%20Notes\"&gt;Page from Sarevok's Notes&lt;/a&gt;. This will reveal a secret room, containing a &lt;a href=\"Shadow%20Aspect\"&gt;Shadow Aspect&lt;/a&gt; and a chest with the Fractal Blade and the unique book &lt;a href=\"Godsbane%20%28book%29\"&gt;Godsbane&lt;/a&gt;. Beware of the traps, too!"}
