{"id": "28778", "revid": "47673695", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=28778", "title": "Dog Meat", "text": "Dog Meat is \"dropped\" after killing the &lt;a href=\"De%27Arnise%20Dogs\"&gt;dogs&lt;/a&gt; in the courtyard of the &lt;a href=\"De%27Arnise%20Keep\"&gt;de'Arnise Keep&lt;/a&gt;. It is the required ingredient in the creation of &lt;a href=\"Dog%20Stew\"&gt;dog stew&lt;/a&gt;, which is cooked up if the cauldron that's on the wood range in the kitchen and then fed to the &lt;a href=\"Umber%20Hulk\"&gt;Umber Hulk&lt;/a&gt;s that are located in the cellar of the Keep."}
{"id": "30113", "revid": "46775035", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=30113", "title": "Dog Stew", "text": "Dog Stew is fed to the &lt;a href=\"Umber%20Hulk\"&gt;Umber Hulk&lt;/a&gt;s in the cellar of the &lt;a href=\"De%27Arnise%20Keep\"&gt;de'Arnise Keep&lt;/a&gt; by the stable boy &lt;a href=\"Daleson\"&gt;Daleson&lt;/a&gt;. It is created using the cauldron on the wood range in the kitchen after first killing the four &lt;a href=\"De%27Arnise%20Dogs\"&gt;dogs&lt;/a&gt; in the courtyard and then gathering the &lt;a href=\"Dog%20Meat\"&gt;dog meat&lt;/a&gt; from each corpse. Cook the meat in the cauldron and voil\u00e0...dog stew."}
