{"id": "23739", "revid": "275010", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=23739", "title": "Dragonscale Armor", "text": "Dragonscale Armor is in \"\".\nAcquisition.\nThe armor can be crafted by &lt;a href=\"Jegg%20Hillcarver\"&gt;Jegg Hillcarver&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"Bridgefort\"&gt;Bridgefort&lt;/a&gt; from the &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Scales\"&gt;Dragon Scales&lt;/a&gt; of &lt;a href=\"Morentherene\"&gt;Morentherene&lt;/a&gt;. It is mutually exclusive with gaining the &lt;a href=\"Dragonscale%20Shield\"&gt;Dragonscale Shield&lt;/a&gt;.\nGameplay.\nThis armor offers non-magical protection from poison, both from the &lt;a href=\"status%20effect\"&gt;status effect&lt;/a&gt; and the direct poison damage.\nBecause it is non-magical, it may be used with items that magically boost armor class, such as a &lt;a href=\"Cloak%20of%20Protection%20%2B1\"&gt;Cloak of Protection +1&lt;/a&gt; or a &lt;a href=\"The%20Guard%27s%20Ring\"&gt;Ring of Protection +2&lt;/a&gt;.\nAs it\u00a0is not made from metal, it can be worn by &lt;a href=\"Druid\"&gt;Druid&lt;/a&gt;s.\nNotable reaction.\nThe &lt;a href=\"Young%20Green%20Dragon\"&gt;Young Green Dragon&lt;/a&gt; is not amused if a &lt;a href=\"party\"&gt;party&lt;/a&gt; member is using this armor or the &lt;a href=\"Dragonscale%20Shield\"&gt;Dragonscale Shield&lt;/a&gt; equipped when meeting him during a &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20vs.%20Giants%20Waylay\"&gt;random travel encounter&lt;/a&gt;."}
{"id": "25803", "revid": "46775035", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=25803", "title": "Dragonscale Shield", "text": "Dragonscale Shield is a in \"\".\nAcquisition.\nThe shield can be crafted by\u00a0&lt;a href=\"Jegg\"&gt;Jegg Hillcarver&lt;/a&gt;\u00a0in\u00a0&lt;a href=\"Bridgefort\"&gt;Bridgefort&lt;/a&gt;\u00a0from the\u00a0&lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Scales\"&gt;Dragon Scales&lt;/a&gt;\u00a0of\u00a0&lt;a href=\"Morentherene\"&gt;Morentherene&lt;/a&gt;.\nThis item is mutually exclusive with &lt;a href=\"Dragonscale%20Armor\"&gt;Dragonscale Armor&lt;/a&gt;.\nReactions.\nThe &lt;a href=\"Young%20Green%20Dragon\"&gt;Young Green Dragon&lt;/a&gt; is not amused if a &lt;a href=\"party\"&gt;party&lt;/a&gt; member is using this shield or the &lt;a href=\"Dragonscale%20Armor\"&gt;Dragonscale Armor&lt;/a&gt; equipped when meeting him during a &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20vs.%20Giants%20Waylay\"&gt;random travel encounter&lt;/a&gt;."}
