{"id": "9198", "revid": "47673695", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=9198", "title": "Drow Crossbow of Speed", "text": "Drow Crossbow of Speed (Drow Crossbow of Speed +3 in-game) is an enchanted light crossbow +3 in terms of enchantment. Like all adamantine items, this will turn into &lt;a href=\"Adamantine%20Dust\"&gt;Adamantine Dust&lt;/a&gt; when it's taken out of the Underdark.\nThis weapon is nearly the same as the &lt;a href=\"Light%20Crossbow%20of%20Speed\"&gt;Light Crossbow of Speed&lt;/a&gt;, but since the mentioned crossbow is a +1 weapon, the drow variant weapon with +3 bonus to damage and -3 THAC0 with a speed factor of 1, is a lot better. But the +1 crossbow isn't made of adamantine and therefore can be used anywhere.\nThe &lt;a href=\"Drow%20Assassin\"&gt;Drow Assassin&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Drow%20War%20Scout\"&gt;Drow War Scout&lt;/a&gt; can drop this weapon in , and &lt;a href=\"Drow\"&gt;Drow&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Drow%20Warrior%20%28Underdark%29\"&gt;Drow Warrior (Underdark)&lt;/a&gt; can also drop this weapon in and . The Drow Warriors in &lt;a href=\"Sendai%27s%20Enclave\"&gt;Sendai's Enclave&lt;/a&gt; in also employ these weapons. Most drow fire &lt;a href=\"Drow%20Bolt\"&gt;Drow Bolt&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Drow%20Bolt%20of%20Sleep\"&gt;Drow Bolt of Sleep&lt;/a&gt; and or &lt;a href=\"Drow%20Bolt%20of%20Stunning\"&gt;Drow Bolt of Stunning&lt;/a&gt; from this crossbow. A typical warrior will have a quiver with two kinds of ammunition available."}
