{"id": "5051", "revid": "8506165", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=5051", "title": "Drow Elven Chain", "text": "Drow Elven Chain is enchanted elven chain mail +3 which bestows an armor class of 2 upon the wearer. It also gives the wearer a 5% magic resistance bonus and reduces the speed factor of all spells by 1. &lt;a href=\"Bard\"&gt;Bard&lt;/a&gt;s can wear this and are able to cast spells. &lt;a href=\"thief\"&gt;thieves&lt;/a&gt; can wear this too, but like all &lt;a href=\"Elven%20Chainmail%20Armor\"&gt;elven chain&lt;/a&gt;, it lowers &lt;a href=\"Thieving%20Abilities\"&gt;Thieving Abilities&lt;/a&gt;.\nIt has the same protection modifiers as normal &lt;a href=\"Chainmail%20Armor\"&gt;chain mail&lt;/a&gt;. The armor will dissolve to &lt;a href=\"Adamantine%20Dust\"&gt;Adamantine Dust&lt;/a&gt; if it's exposed to sunlight, which can't be avoided by storing the armor in the &lt;a href=\"Bag%20of%20Holding\"&gt;Bag of Holding&lt;/a&gt;."}
{"id": "20048", "revid": "978785", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=20048", "title": "Drow Elven Chain +3", "text": ""}
