{"id": "8814", "revid": "53053884", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=8814", "title": "Dryad of the Cloud Peaks (quest)", "text": "Dryad of the Cloud Peaks is a quest with a moral, and the moral is: don't be greedy. When a &lt;a href=\"Dryad%20of%20the%20Cloud%20Peaks\"&gt;nice dryad&lt;/a&gt; asks for your help, just do it. Asking for payment or, worse yet, \"insisting\" on payment will only reduce your eventual reward. The possible rewards are:\nOther rewards include 175 xp each for killing &lt;a href=\"Caldo\"&gt;Caldo&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Krumm\"&gt;Krumm&lt;/a&gt;, a &lt;a href=\"Girdle%20of%20Bluntness\"&gt;Girdle of Bluntness&lt;/a&gt; (AC +4 vs. blunt weapons) from the body of Krumm.\nAlternatively, side with the thugs and the dryad turns hostile. Kill her for 975 xp, the &lt;a href=\"Antidote\"&gt;Antidote&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Potion%20of%20Healing\"&gt;Potion of Healing&lt;/a&gt; both, as well as a &lt;a href=\"Dagger\"&gt;Dagger&lt;/a&gt;, but suffer a major loss to &lt;a href=\"Reputation\"&gt;Reputation&lt;/a&gt;.\u00a0(See \"Killing an innocent\" in the\u00a0&lt;a href=\"Reputation%23Effects%20of%20Actions%20on%20reputation%20table\"&gt;Effects of Actions on reputation table&lt;/a&gt;.)"}
