{"id": "8451", "revid": "47673695", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=8451", "title": "Bellamy", "text": "Bellamy is a &lt;a href=\"halfling\"&gt;halfling&lt;/a&gt; bard who can be found on the ground floor of the &lt;a href=\"Three%20Old%20Kegs\"&gt;Three Old Kegs&lt;/a&gt;, an inn that's located in &lt;a href=\"North%20Baldur%27s%20Gate\"&gt;North Baldur's Gate&lt;/a&gt;.\nDepending on the &lt;a href=\"party\"&gt;party&lt;/a&gt;'s &lt;a href=\"reputation\"&gt;reputation&lt;/a&gt;, he will warn them about &lt;a href=\"Phandalyn\"&gt;Phandalyn&lt;/a&gt; \u2013 a paladin who will attack any party with at least one evil &lt;a href=\"Alignment\"&gt;aligned&lt;/a&gt; member \u2013 or simply greet them by saying \"Good day to ya\" and then walk away.\nIf the warning was given then the following &lt;a href=\"Journal\"&gt;Journal&lt;/a&gt; entry will be made:"}
{"id": "49779", "revid": "44830706", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=49779", "title": "Belle", "text": "Belle is a human female fighter in the &lt;a href=\"Five%20Flagons%20Inn\"&gt;Five Flagons Inn&lt;/a&gt; located in the &lt;a href=\"Bridge%20District\"&gt;Bridge District&lt;/a&gt;. She is clad in Splint Mail and holds a Two-handed sword. Belle has some dialogue if you speak with her. She seems to be a tough-minded no-nonsense warrior. She has some minor treasure in her pockets.\nThere are special lines of commentary for &lt;a href=\"Mazzy%20Fentan\"&gt;Mazzy Fentan&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Viconia%20DeVir\"&gt;Viconia DeVir&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Valygar%20Corthala\"&gt;Valygar Corthala&lt;/a&gt;, but those party members must initiate the conversation.\nMod content.\n&lt;a href=\"Sword%20Coast%20Stratagems\"&gt;Sword Coast Stratagems&lt;/a&gt; revises Belle by assigning an SCS default fighter AI script for smarter tactical behavior. Weapon proficiency is changed to 4 pips with Two-handed sword and 2 pips in Two-handed fighting style. Random SCS treasures are placed in her inventory."}
{"id": "42937", "revid": "3077225", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=42937", "title": "Bellowgulp", "text": ""}
