{"id": "8679", "revid": "47673695", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=8679", "title": "Black Lily", "text": "Black Lily is a &lt;a href=\"Thieves%27%20Guild\"&gt;thieves' guild&lt;/a&gt; merchant in the city of &lt;a href=\"Baldur%27s%20Gate%20%28city%29\"&gt;Baldur's Gate&lt;/a&gt;. She operates out of the far right house, which is part of the multitude of houses located just north of &lt;a href=\"Sorcerous%20Sundries\"&gt;Sorcerous Sundries&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"East%20Baldur%27s%20Gate\"&gt;East Baldur's Gate&lt;/a&gt;, that represent the thieves' guild headquarters in the city. \nFrom the inside she can be found in a small store room located right off the main room near the stairs to the basement. However \u2014 she's the single most expensive store in the game, so you may want to stock up elsewhere.\nIf you use charm magic on her and succeed, speak to her and she will say the following:\nExpanded Thief Stronghold.\nThe mod \"&lt;a href=\"Expanded%20Thief%20Stronghold\"&gt;Expanded Thief Stronghold&lt;/a&gt;\" adds a quest in the &lt;a href=\"Thieves%27%20Guild%20Stronghold\"&gt;Thieves' Guild Stronghold&lt;/a&gt; of \"\" in which Black Lily and &lt;a href=\"Narlen%20Darkwalk\"&gt;Narlen Darkwalk&lt;/a&gt; appear in &lt;a href=\"Athkatla\"&gt;Athkatla&lt;/a&gt;. After the quest is solved, Black Lily provides her services at the thieves guild."}
