{"id": "30610", "revid": "47673695", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=30610", "title": "Black Pits Flyer", "text": "This Black Pits Flyer is an advertisement for &lt;a href=\"Baeloth%20Barrityl\"&gt;Baeloth's&lt;/a&gt; latest incarnation of his &lt;a href=\"The%20Black%20Pits\"&gt;Black Pits&lt;/a&gt; entertainment scheme. This one is a single shallow pit located along the banks of the Winding Water river, downstream from the Coast Way Crossing bridge.\nA flyer can be obtained from the &lt;a href=\"Announcer\"&gt;Announcer&lt;/a&gt; or the drop items left by one of the &lt;a href=\"Crusader%20Guard\"&gt;Crusader Guards&lt;/a&gt; who are killed in the cut scene during the destruction of the bridge.\nVisiting the location presents the player with the opportunity to recruit Baeloth and a new companion &lt;a href=\"M%27Khiin%20Grubdoubler\"&gt;M'Khiin Grubdoubler&lt;/a&gt; into the party."}
