{"id": "5125", "revid": "44830706", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=5125", "title": "Bolt of Glory", "text": "Bolt of Glory is a 6th level &lt;a href=\"priest%20spell\"&gt;priest spell&lt;/a&gt; that creates a bolt of holy energy which deals serious damage against the targeted creature.\nGameplay.\nAs a single target spell, any spell protection that can deflect or turn a level 6 spell will stop it, such as &lt;a href=\"Spell%20Deflection\"&gt;Spell Deflection&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Spell%20Immunity\"&gt;Spell Immunity&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Spell%20Turning\"&gt;Spell Turning&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href=\"Spell%20Trap\"&gt;Spell Trap&lt;/a&gt;.\n and are not affected by the spell. The &lt;a href=\"Cloak%20of%20Mirroring\"&gt;Cloak of Mirroring&lt;/a&gt; will send it back to the originator or deflect it .\nThe spell inflicts &lt;a href=\"Magical%20damage\"&gt;Magical damage&lt;/a&gt;. It is one of the few spells which bypasses &lt;a href=\"magic%20resistance\"&gt;magic resistance&lt;/a&gt;.\nMod content.\n&lt;a href=\"Spell%20Revisions\"&gt;Spell Revisions&lt;/a&gt; mod has changed this divine spell, revising its effects, casting time and description. See below:\nBolt of Glory\nLevel: 6\nSchool: Evocation\nSphere: Combat, Summoning\nRange: Long\nDuration: Instant\nCasting Time: 6\nArea of Effect: 1 creature\nSaving Throw: None\nBy casting this spell, the priest channels a bolt of divine energy against one creature. No attack roll is needed. Creatures struck suffer varying damage, depending on their plane of existence.\nCreature Type \u2013 Damage\nElemental \u2013 4d4\nHumanoid \u2013 6d6\nUndead \u2013 8d8\nDemonic \u2013 10d10\nMagic resistance does not affect this spell."}
