{"id": "8994", "revid": "44830706", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=8994", "title": "Boneblade", "text": "Boneblade is a level 4 enchanted dagger. This item appears in and . \nGameplay.\nThis dagger can inflict 1d4 +4 points of &lt;a href=\"Piercing%20damage\"&gt;Piercing damage&lt;/a&gt; damage, a 4 point &lt;a href=\"THAC0\"&gt;THAC0&lt;/a&gt; bonus, a speed factor of 0 and it weighs 1 pound.\nAquisition.\nIt is dropped by &lt;a href=\"Qilue\"&gt;Qilue&lt;/a&gt; in her &lt;a href=\"Qilue%27s%20Home\"&gt;home&lt;/a&gt; when you kill her under &lt;a href=\"Aboleth\"&gt;Aboleth&lt;/a&gt;'s orders in the &lt;a href=\"Ust%20Natha\"&gt;Ust Natha&lt;/a&gt;.\nIn order to gain access to Qilue, the party must accept the &lt;a href=\"Retrieve%20Qilue%27s%20Brain\"&gt;Retrieve Qilue's Brain&lt;/a&gt; quest, and pickpocket or defeat her."}
