{"id": "8017", "revid": "47673695", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=8017", "title": "Brevlik", "text": "Brevlik is a shifty &lt;a href=\"gnome\"&gt;gnome&lt;/a&gt; who can be found in the &lt;a href=\"Elfsong%20Tavern\"&gt;Elfsong Tavern&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"East%20Baldur%27s%20Gate\"&gt;East Baldur's Gate&lt;/a&gt;. If you choose to speak to him he'll proposition you with a request to thieve an item from the &lt;a href=\"Hall%20of%20Wonders\"&gt;Hall of Wonders&lt;/a&gt;.\nIf you refuse his quest and meet him later, he will ask you to buy his ring so that he can pay his bill at the inn. The ring is &lt;a href=\"Discipliner\"&gt;Discipliner&lt;/a&gt;.\nSide quests.\n&lt;a href=\"Larceny%20at%20the%20Hall%20of%20Wonders\"&gt;Larceny at the Hall of Wonders&lt;/a&gt;.\nBrevlik hires &lt;a href=\"Gorion%27s%20Ward\"&gt;Gorion's Ward&lt;/a&gt; and party to steal a &lt;a href=\"telescope\"&gt;telescope&lt;/a&gt; that's on display at the Hall of Wonders.\nWith the right choices during the conversation, he will hand out twice and raise the reward for the quest to , plus a &lt;a href=\"Wand%20of%20Lightning\"&gt;Wand of Lightning&lt;/a&gt; on top. Conversation choices to get the most rewards: 1, 3, 4, 4, 3, 2, 3, 3, 3.\nOr you can just pickpocket the wand and move on if you don't want the extra errand. The wand has 13 charges."}
