{"id": "45597", "revid": "773742", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=45597", "title": "Yi Kwon", "text": "Yi Kwon is one of the six lieutenants of &lt;a href=\"Nan%20Kung%20Chi\"&gt;Nan Kung Chi&lt;/a&gt;. &lt;a href=\"Ki%20Chin%20Sang\"&gt;Ki Chin Sang&lt;/a&gt; asks &lt;a href=\"Gorion%27s%20Ward\"&gt;Gorion's Ward&lt;/a&gt; to slay Nan Kung Chi's lieutenants to prove himself and be deemed worthy of receiving the &lt;a href=\"Key%20of%20the%20Master%27s%20Crypt\"&gt;key&lt;/a&gt; to Nan Kung Chi's tomb. Yi Kwon has all the special abilities and immunities afforded to a &lt;a href=\"Monk\"&gt;Monk&lt;/a&gt; of his experience level, plus 42% magic resistance. He attacks with his fists and feet and will use his special abilities such as &lt;a href=\"Stunning%20Blow\"&gt;Stunning Blow&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Quivering%20Palm\"&gt;Quivering Palm&lt;/a&gt;. This monk can see invisible creatures."}
{"id": "45594", "revid": "773742", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=45594", "title": "Yi Niu", "text": "Yi Niu is one of the six lieutenants of &lt;a href=\"Nan%20Kung%20Chi\"&gt;Nan Kung Chi&lt;/a&gt;. &lt;a href=\"Ki%20Chin%20Sang\"&gt;Ki Chin Sang&lt;/a&gt; asks &lt;a href=\"Gorion%27s%20Ward\"&gt;Gorion's Ward&lt;/a&gt; to slay Nan Kung Chi's lieutenants to prove himself and be deemed worthy of receiving the &lt;a href=\"Key%20of%20the%20Master%27s%20Crypt\"&gt;key&lt;/a&gt; to Nan Kung Chi's tomb. Yi Niu is protected from poison, haste and slow effects, charm effects and disease effects. She wears an undroppable &lt;a href=\"Ring%20of%20Duplication\"&gt;Ring of Duplication&lt;/a&gt; as well."}
